Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:27.92,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H5742BB&\4c&H5742BB&}まさか　いや　片思い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:26.71,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両思い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:30.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やばい！　視線合っちゃった！！！
