Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好餓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.15,0:00:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.71,0:00:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿她沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 這種程度的陷阱我就中一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連獵物都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.15,0:00:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中招了！ 中招了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挨了一悶棍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.15,0:00:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這明明是準備中午吃的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有菜了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是共犯哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為阪本說想吃才…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.89,0:00:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.16,0:00:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒說過哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼你亂說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:00:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你都吃了嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.94,0:00:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}今天好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.27,0:00:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}是好熱吶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.97,0:01:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}回去的路上去站前吃冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.00,0:01:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}好啊 好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦誒 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.74,0:01:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘想去學校吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不想讓你去呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.40,0:01:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼突然這個樣子？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.40,0:01:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說名乃你要去別的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.76,0:01:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？誰說的這些話啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的才不是那回事呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.18,0:01:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃 你要去哪裡麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是準備上午去買東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯的菜都沒有了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.57,0:01:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士我也要去 要去～！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我什麼都不買哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.65,0:01:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買鯊魚巧克力吧～！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不買
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}買吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}鯊魚巧克力…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不會買的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買吧 買吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}才不會買！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本都說買吧了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.18,0:01:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒說喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 小祐！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從早上起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼一說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 語法形式都崩壞了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也有點發燒…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼身體狀況都這樣了還來上學啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不… 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:03:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是說過了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:04:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想 要給你變個魔術什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種是我第一次聽到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}嘔——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 現在不是說魔術的時候吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易練習來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了我的魔術的話一定要大吃一驚哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘔——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話我現在就大吃一驚了喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先回到座位…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到道具了啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先裝作什麼都沒看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟身體都這樣了還要硬撐著來…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小祐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你準備連續放出什麼大招呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出出 出出 出來了啊——！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道具都跑出來了啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛跑啦——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擤鼻涕紙——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好·的 那開始了哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O… OK～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔哇 我在做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺就藏起來了哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那——個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼… 首先是——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有注意到鴿子和手杖…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底多虛弱了喲… 你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先來個煙穿百元幣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開著呢！！洞啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…看見了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紅桃A啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼… 從嘴裡面…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛出來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了些… 什麼手腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我去超市了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！博士也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你搗蛋來著 今天什麼都不給你買哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本 你真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說你啊 你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 咱們走吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃你要買什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 還是魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士買些什麼呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！？ 博士今天不可以哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒～？ 那不買零食了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零食之外的東西也不可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不知道買什麼好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是想買東西吶…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(606,558)\shad1\c&H6FFDFA&\3c&H4590E7&\4c&H132E50&}鯊魚蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃～ 是鯊魚蛋糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個臨時攤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很好吃的樣子 買來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你忘了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒～？你看 我想給阪本一份禮品來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生也跟著搗亂來著所以不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是想給名乃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才說錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了不可以就是不可以的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要是太寵她的話 以後又會做出同樣的事情來吶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來 博士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}給我買…×N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}給我買…×N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}給我買…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}給我買…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}給我買…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在一定要狠下心來！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在該…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 不行不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一點點的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！不行！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 不行不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是給她買了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 敗給她了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小鬼不管別人說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都愛亂使性子恣意妄為啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是該給她提個醒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦誒 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多你也該學學怎麼忍耐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白你妹哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東雲家 今天也很和睦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:18.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,0)\fs70\pos(1200,195)}80\N分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:18.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,0)\fs70\frz270\pos(1200,428)}Mongolian
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}註：這裡的Mongolian指Mongolian chop 雙手同時打擊對方鎖骨的一種拳擊招式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害哦 得了80分！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真點的話你也很厲害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～ 啊哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼 得高分的秘訣是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒沒沒 哪有什麼秘訣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒～？可以的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教教我秘訣嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐… 我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}80分 哎呦喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:41.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,520)\bord4\blur8\pos(1100,360)}秘\N\N訣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我教給你得80分的秘訣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省了吧 我得了96分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,80分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅持不懈的努力和…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEART喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好煩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:10:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy110\fad(900,0)\fs66\c&HFAF9FB&\blur20\t(0,900,1\blur1)\bord0\shad4\pos(640,550)\4c&H74907A&\3c&HE0E7E1&}差強人意的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\c&H424043&}「相生」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\c&H424043&}「唔唔唔唔…」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\c&H424043&}「誒…？」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\c&H424043&}「誒誒…？」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord0\c&H424043&}「太好啦——！！」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\shad0\bord0\c&H424043&\frz25.389\move(338,212,281,224)}國語小測
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,520)\bord4\blur9\pos(800,360)}現\N\N實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你做飯來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 還在旅行中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 幫大忙囉！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 小美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 今天就陪孫子玩一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉厭煩的現實吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美 今天玩點什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.09,0:11:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個先別管了 印章在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 印章在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏在哪裡了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 告訴我嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這書架上嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 印章在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}吶吶 在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這… 比現實更加過分啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}哪裡哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}快出來——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為定的幾點見面啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著乘公交車去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:12:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果乘上時代之洪流了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走到御徒町站算了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}御徒盯站：位於東京都台東區的東日本旅客鐵道的一站
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶～ 名乃～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神馬事啊？博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要去尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃也一起去吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶～ 去吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 去吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶～ 名～乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 吶～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼呼呼呼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 才不對喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不對？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俄羅斯紅菜湯是食物喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 不是那件事啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去尿尿吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 名乃～ 名乃 吶～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你… 難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 只有一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 你趕緊去廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為擔心她而沒有說出來的阪本是也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 沒有辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才說小鬼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這深夜狂風裡一個人去廁所更加不可能啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就應該
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她說我跟著一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這傢伙再次認識到我的可貴之處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦誒 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法吶 我跟你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本又小又很弱的樣子 還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘想去學校吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 過來這邊了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去尿尿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了 我倒是不太想去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微有點害怕啊 一起去吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 把我叫起來不就好了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫了你好多遍了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「咚咚」的好響…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能有人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是上面的煙囪在響吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過說起來雨還真大啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 吶～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 博士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打雷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有博士在呢沒關係的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊完事 回到被窩裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是… 一個人的話有點可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起的話好像就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來也是吶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃… 想去學校麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我會一直待在家裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是阪本說名乃想去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥氣的東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,80分！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,900)\pos(652,493)\c&H0A0A0A&\shad0\bord0}隻言片語
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一個月很快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期日卻很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:35.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,520)\shad2\pos(100,360)\4c&HE4E4E4&}興\N致\N勃\N勃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站是～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,80分 80分～～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在～右側下車～～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來給你唱80年代的曲目哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只唱80分 噗噗噗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,80分 哎呦喂…x3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我墜入伊甸吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:56.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord4\blur8\pos(800,360)}伊\N\N甸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 靜一靜啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在發表這一次的平均分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,92分！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這一下子的幹嘛啊 小鬼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別玩了 來幫忙整理洗好的衣服吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始 你可以去學校了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然間這是怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是博士我的妙計
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦——！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來白天吃多少零食都不會被罵囉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話就不能背雙背帶書包了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去上高中哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是博士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把發條拿下來的話 去學校就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是名乃的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡博士了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃×N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士×N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃×N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士×N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃×N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士×N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃～～      博士～～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃～～      博士～～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃名乃～～      博士博士～～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃～～      博士～～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.97,0:23:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是萬國旗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常會聽到BANKOKKI和BANKOKUKI兩種念法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像兩種念法都是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.38,0:23:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸最後說過「細節就不要在意了」…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.65,0:23:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話是第十四話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.74,0:23:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.81,0:22:08.73,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}朝起きて　歯を磨いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.98,0:22:11.73,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}あっという間　午後10時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:15.03,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今日も　たくさん　笑ったなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.19,0:22:17.78,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}たくさん　ときめいたなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.32,0:22:21.24,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}友達と　バカみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.41,0:22:24.16,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}騒いでる　時にも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.49,0:22:27.50,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}チラチラって　目が合う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.62,0:22:30.21,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}…偶然、だよね。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.42,0:22:33.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}初恋なんて言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.88,0:22:36.84,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}キャラじゃないんだもんっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.01,0:22:42.84,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}ねえ　あしたも会えるよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.09,0:22:45.93,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}まぶたを　閉じると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.18,0:22:49.14,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}キラキラ　キミだらけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:52.44,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今日も　楽しかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:56.86,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}あー　恋　してんだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:04.87,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}うれしいな　うれしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:07.83,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}はじめまして　こいごころ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.16,0:23:11.04,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}あした　まだ　あえるね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:13.71,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}おやすみなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.42,0:23:18.46,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}ゆめで　すぐ　あえるね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.09,0:23:24.64,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\blur3}おやすみなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.81,0:22:08.73,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}早晨睡醒後 起床刷牙來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.98,0:22:11.73,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}不知不覺間 已到晚十點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:15.03,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今天也遇到 很多歡樂事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.19,0:22:17.78,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}也有非常多 刺激與緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.32,0:22:21.24,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}和閨中密友 像笨蛋一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.41,0:22:24.16,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}大聲吵又鬧 偶爾會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.49,0:22:27.50,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}偶爾瞥向你 四目便相接
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.62,0:22:30.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}這也不過是 偶然事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.42,0:22:33.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}初戀什麼的難以說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.88,0:22:36.84,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}因為我不是這樣的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.01,0:22:42.84,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}吶 我們明天 也會相見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.09,0:22:45.93,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}將我的雙眼 合上了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.18,0:22:49.14,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}腦海中只有 亮晶晶的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:52.44,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今天的我也 開心又愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:56.86,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}啊 陷入戀愛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:04.87,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}真的好開心 真的好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:07.83,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}第一次見面 我的愛慕心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.16,0:23:11.04,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}到明天的話 我們又見面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:13.71,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}現在晚安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.42,0:23:18.46,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}在夢中很快 我們會見面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.09,0:23:24.64,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\blur3}現在晚安吧


